# butterflyCurve

- _butterflyCurve(θ)_

Implement the butterfly curve parametric equation.

Plot the butterfly curve, _θ=(0,12π)_:

~~~spl svg=A
(0 -- 12.pi).functionPlot(
	500,
	butterflyCurve:/1
)
~~~

